  "detailed_description": "<strong>ONLINE MULTIPLAYER SHOOTER</strong><br>Only 1 winner. Play a more lethal game of Lasertag with up to 9 friends!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1189060/extras/1b884511fc88e04369a13a209ce27b93.poster.avif?t=1734879606\" width=600 height=194 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1189060/extras/1b884511fc88e04369a13a209ce27b93.webm?t=1734879606\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1189060/extras/1b884511fc88e04369a13a209ce27b93.mp4?t=1734879606\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>EXPLOSIONS! EXPLOSIONS! EXPLOSIONS!</strong><br>Tons of explosives to explode your friends!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1189060/extras/25a34af5fcee503fdcb562e299b7efc6.poster.avif?t=1734879606\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1189060/extras/25a34af5fcee503fdcb562e299b7efc6.webm?t=1734879606\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1189060/extras/25a34af5fcee503fdcb562e299b7efc6.mp4?t=1734879606\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>CUSTOM GAMEMODES</strong><br>Control game settings or play premade gamemodes, like, Hot Potato, Hide and Seek, or the Floor is Lava!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Hide and Seek</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1189060/extras/5b2d6a6f2f64ae339b62fc16e8bbf8ad.poster.avif?t=1734879606\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1189060/extras/5b2d6a6f2f64ae339b62fc16e8bbf8ad.webm?t=1734879606\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1189060/extras/5b2d6a6f2f64ae339b62fc16e8bbf8ad.mp4?t=1734879606\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Hot Potato</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1189060/extras/7a36fa670b852242c8130c75d50cbb29.poster.avif?t=1734879606\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1189060/extras/7a36fa670b852242c8130c75d50cbb29.webm?t=1734879606\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1189060/extras/7a36fa670b852242c8130c75d50cbb29.mp4?t=1734879606\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The Floor Is Lava</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1189060/extras/3a21af52b4d6e7a2f01061a55b1fa4ee.poster.avif?t=1734879606\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1189060/extras/3a21af52b4d6e7a2f01061a55b1fa4ee.webm?t=1734879606\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1189060/extras/3a21af52b4d6e7a2f01061a55b1fa4ee.mp4?t=1734879606\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>WEAPONS AND GADGETS</strong><br>There are over 100 weapons and gedgets, to unlock and play with!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1189060/extras/75392fde6698103dfb209e92095763d2.poster.avif?t=1734879606\" width=600 height=200 ><so